(11, 'VERY IMPORTANT - Rules for Passport Scan', '7', '<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please send all Passport SCAN COPIES FOR UMRAH VISA PROCESSING on this email id only</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><strong>visadepartment500@gmail.com</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SUBJECT of Email should be</strong>&nbsp; :: DELHI :: 205654 :: 13th SEPT :: 04 Pax<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (Departure City :: Booking id :: Travel Date :: Total Pax)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>NOTE ::&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n1. Passport scan should be in PDF or JPG format only.<br />\r\n2. One Passport SIZE Latest Photo on white Background.<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; Size :: 4kb Dimensions :: (148 Width * 174) Height pixels.<br />\r\n3. Attach a Excel Sheet mentioning with Name list, Passport Number and Relation.<br />\r\n4. Pancard copies of the Clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nFor PASSPORT SCAN COPIES - For UMRAH VISA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ONCE YOU HAVE EMAILED THE SCAN COPIES...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please&nbsp; take confirmation on following Mobile What-supp ::+91 93 725 4555 9</p>\r\n\r\n<p>or Call Direct Landline :: 022 - 23407722 :: Visa Department&nbsp;<br />\r\n(Hanzala, Umair, Farhan, Sumaiya)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please Note SCAN COPIES SHOULD BE Very CLEAR and READABLE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Only if above conditions are met we will process passports on SOFT COPIES.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nRegards</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nImran R Shaikh</p>\r\n', 0, '2019-10-07', 1, '2019-10-07 00:00:00', '2019-10-07 00:00:00', NULL),
(13, 'HOTELS FOR OUR GROUPS', '7', '<div>Dear Friends,</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Please Note that we have above <span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><strong>Hotels for our GROUPS</strong></span> but in some situations we may give SIMILAR hotels to our GROUP HOTELS that is why we have written <strong>OR SIMILAR</strong> in our VOUCHERS,</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Like if we dont get <span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><strong>ANWAR DEAFA</strong> </span>we can give <strong>TALA AL BADAR or SIMILAR </strong>hotel.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Like if we dont get <span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><strong>MIRA AJYAAD</strong></span> we can give <strong>ANWAR DEAFA or SIMILAR</strong> hotel.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Like if we dont get<span style=\"color:#0000CD\"> <strong>RIYAD DEAFA </strong></span>we can give <strong>SAFEER DEAFA or SIMILAR </strong>hotel.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>You have to mention and make your haji understand the meaning of or similar</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Regards</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Imran Rahat Shaikh</div>\r\n', 0, '2019-10-16', 1, '2019-10-16 00:00:00', '2019-10-16 00:00:00', NULL),
(14, 'Spelling Mistakes on E-VISA', '6', '<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><strong>Spelling Mistakes on E-VISA</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Friends,<br />\r\nAll our<span style=\"color:#0000CD\"> <strong>Visas are processed at least 5 days before Departure</strong></span><br />\r\nYou are <strong>REQUESTED</strong> to please make <span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><strong>Full payment before 5 days </strong></span>and collect your <span style=\"color:#0000CD\"><strong>VISAS &amp; CHECK THEM</strong></span> for any MISTAKES - Mehram Mistakes, Spelling Mistakes, Photo Mistakes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will <span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><strong>NOT BE RESPONSIBLE</strong> </span>for any Guest Missing the flights if you did not check the VISAS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If their are <strong><span style=\"color:#0000CD\">ANY MISTAKE</span></strong> we need a MESSAGE in your Whatsupp GROUP only that will hold good.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regards</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imran Rahat Shaikh</p>\r\n', 0, '2019-10-16', 1, '2019-10-16 00:00:00', '2019-10-16 00:00:00', NULL),
(15, 'ANNOUNCED UMRAH PACKAGE', '7', '<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Alhamdulillah<br />\r\nPlease note that we <strong>ANNOUNCED UMRAH PACKAGE</strong> now for FULL SEASON<br />\r\n- We have BLUE AND RED FLIERS Till <strong>31st MARCH 2020</strong><br />\r\n- THEN WE HAVE <strong>SHABAAN + RAMZAAN</strong> on YELLOW FLIERS.<br />\r\n- THEN WE HAVE <strong>FULL RAMZAAN&nbsp; FLIERS</strong> on same YELLOW FLIERS.<br />\r\n- THEN WE HAVE <strong>RAMZAAN&nbsp; + SHAWWAL</strong> on same YELLOW FLIERS.<br />\r\n- THEN WE HAVE <strong>SHORT HAJJ + LONG HAJJ</strong> Separate FLIERS.&nbsp;<br />\r\n-- Also we keep sending SPECIAL OFFERS as and when we get cheap fares..</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Do Remember RAHAT se RAHAT HAI...</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\">Please Note if you need any <strong>HOTEL PICS or VIDEOS</strong> do send me Whatsspp on my <strong>personal number +91 8879453555</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Daily HOTEL And Pics and VIDEO Updates can be checked on our Facebook page :</strong>:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>https://www.facebook.com/rahattravelsofindia/</strong></span></p>\r\n', 0, '2019-11-07', 1, '2019-11-07 00:00:00', '2019-11-07 00:00:00', NULL),
(16, 'VERY IMPORTANT NOTE', '7', '<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>VERY IMPORTANT NOTE</strong><br />\r\n<strong>- UNUSED Services in UMRAH PACKAGE will not be REFUNDED</strong><br />\r\nWe cannot have anyone saying that we have not used your laundry services&nbsp;<br />\r\nor we dont like your food we need refund for that service</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>- PACKAGE Change in between ongoing Tour is Not possible</strong><br />\r\nPackage change is possible only 7 days before Travel<br />\r\nIf you have booked in BUDGET you cannot go to saudi and tell me i need to Change to&nbsp;<br />\r\nDeluxe and i am ready to pay the difference. That cannot be done.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>- All Special Offers are with 100% Non Refundable payment</strong><br />\r\nYou cannot deposit 5000 or 10000 and ask me to hold seats for you<br />\r\nBecoz special offers are from LCC Carriers &amp; AIRLINES that do not hold seats.</span></p>\r\n', 0, '2019-11-07', 1, '2019-11-07 00:00:00', '2019-11-07 00:00:00', NULL);

